description:
The 23nd edition of Founders Are Happy [Hour] will be dedicated to 3 amazing Founders Founders residents, Acsendo, Emitu & FES Agency.
This time the Happy Hour will take place at 3 smaller offices – but don’t get the wrong idea, although they’re physically small they do not lack greatness. Come and meet their lovely projects and teams. Join us for drinks, snacks and for some chat about their tech and business.
name: Founders Are Happy [Hour] #24 at Acsendo, Emitu & FES Agency
